spec_data.Name: perl-Mozilla-PublicSuffix
spec_data.Description:
This module provides a single function that returns the public suffix of a
domain name by referencing a parsed copy of Mozilla's Public Suffix List.
From the official website at http://publicsuffix.org/
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 02:12:14 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Get a domain name's public suffix via the Mozilla Public Suffix List
